        #=========================
# format of ion file
#=========================
# ATOM_TYPE:   <atom type name> 
# PSEUDO_POT:  <path/to/pseudopotential/>
# N_TYPE_ATOM: <num of atoms of this type>
# ATOMIC_MASS: <mass of atom of this type> #(optional, for MD only)
# COORD:
# <xcoord> <ycoord> <zcoord>
# ...
# RELAX: #(optional)
# <xrelax> <yrelax> <zrelax>
# ...

